{"word":"G1567 - ἐκζητέω - ekzētéō - ek-zay-teh'-o - En- quire","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐκζητέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ekzētéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ek-zay-teh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">En- quire</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தேடு, பரிசோதனை பண்ணு"},{"paragraph":"to seek out, search for"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G2212 - ζητέω - zētéō - dzay-teh'-o/2212\">G2212</a>; to <i>search out</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>investigate</i>, <i>crave</i>, <i>demand</i>, (by Hebraism) <i>worship:</i> - en- (re-) quire, seek after (carefully, diligently).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}